(75714, 'ruRU', 'A Trainee\'s Test [DNT]', 'This is the text that tells the player what to do and where to go.', 'It is time for the trainee to learn how to edit text!\n\nThere are multiple places where text exists.\n\nYou should be aware of all of them.\n\nBeware the red text!', '', 'The murloc is one of the most deadly creatures in all of WoW.', 'Murloc Puddlestomper', '', '', 'This the text that shows up after the player completes the objectives. We usually leave this blank.', 57534),
